      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Script Scope Test\n\nUse this graph to test that scripts only see and mutate the active fragment.\n\nSuggested checks:\n- run a script in the root fragment\n- expand into another fragment\n- verify out-of-scope reads and mutations fail in diagnostics",
        "memo": "",
        "link": "",
        "html": "",
        "svg": "",
        "isRoot": true,
        "root": true
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "script-scope-test-note",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Expected Behavior",
      "position": {
        "x": 260,
        "y": 40
      },
      "width": 380,
      "height": 220,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Expected Behavior\n\n- `getNodes()` returns only active-fragment nodes\n- foreign `getNode(id)` fails with scope error\n- foreign mutations are rejected\n- script failures appear in diagnostics",
        "memo": "",
        "link": "",
        "html": "",
        "svg": "",
        "isRoot": false,
        "root": false
      }
